<p>Tim regales Frank with the tale of <em>Knightfall</em>. This is the story of Bane, the Man Who Broke The Bat! If you enjoyed <em>The Dark Knight Rises</em> or Tim’s recaps of the <em>Arkham</em> games (<a href="http://www.beerwithgeeks.com/2015/07/061-theres-no-crying-in-nanda-parbat.html">here</a> and <a href="http://www.beerwithgeeks.com/2015/07/062-shes-dead-jim.html">here</a>), you’ll love this too!</p>

